data.name: Label3.Text
data.value: 1. This is a list of files. Highlight files (symbols) you wish to analyze. If none appear, click the "Browse" button (3), or add symbols (space separated) to the text box (2) and click "Start" (3). You can select a different portfolio using the "Portfolio" button, too (not shown at 3).

data.name: Label7.Text
data.value: 3. "Help" displays this form. Use "Browse" to locate quote files. "Select All" highlights files in 1. "Start" and "Stop" begin and end the analysis process. "Done" returns you to the Main Form. Not shown are "Clipboard" and "Portfolio" buttons. For the clipboard, highlight rows in 4 and click "Clipboard" to copy the information to the clipboard for pasting into another program like Notepad or Excel. Click "Portfolio" to select a different portfolio to analyze.
